lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton said the latest round of congressional investigations into the 2012 attacks on the U.S. diplomatic post in Benghazi, Libya, would not deter her from seeking the presidency.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Says Benghazi Probes Won't Deter Possible White House Bid
